quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,"Mubalwanyise, Katonda ababonereze n’emikono gya mmwe, era abakkakkanye era mmwe abataase ku bo, aweweeze ekyo ekiri mu mitima gya bakkiriza"
  9,15,"Era amalewo obukyayi bw’emitima gya bwe, era Katonda akkirize okwenenya kw’oyo gwaba ayagadde, bulijjo Katonda muyitirivu w’a kumanya, mugoba nsonga"
  9,16,"Abaffe, musuubidde okuba nga mulekebwa (nemutagezesebwa), Katonda abe nga amanya abo abaalafuubana mu mmwe (olw'ediini), nebateeteerawo wa mukwano yenna atali Katonda, oba omubakawe, oba abakkiriza, bulijjo Katonda amanyidde ddala ebyo bye mukola"
  9,17,"Abagatta ku Katonda e bintu e birala tebakkirizibwa kuzimba mizikiti gya Katonda, nga nabo bennyini beewaako obujulizi nti bakaafiiri, abo e mirimu gya bwe gyonna mifu, era nga mu muliro mwe bagenda okutuula obugenderevu"
  9,18,"Mazima ddala azimba e mizikiti gy’a Katonda, yooyo akkiriza Katonda n’olunaku lw'enkomerero, n’ayimirizaawo e sswala, n'atoola zzaka, era n’atatya okugyako Katonda, abo nno be bookubeera mu balungamu"
  9,19,"Muddira mutya okuwa ba Hajji amazzi n’okulabirira omuzikiti ogw’e mizizo ne mukyenkanya n'oyo akkiriza Katonda n’olunaku lw'enkomerero! era naalafuubana mu kuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda, tebayinza kwenkana mu maaso g’a Katonda, era bulijjo Katonda talungamya bantu beeyisa bubi"
  9,20,"Abo abakkiriza, nebasenguka, era ne balafuubana mu kuweereza mu kkubo lya Katonda nga bakozesa e mmaali yaabwe n'emyoyo gyabwe, be basinga amadaala ag’a waggulu ewa Katonda, era abo, bo be b'okwesiima"